    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest driver with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. Runs, moves, and stops, with a powertrain that feels willing and a chassis that still tracks confidently. Not a show car, but a solid budget-friendly project, commuter, or parts-friendly platform for someone who appreciates a mechanically straightforward setup. Cosmetic wear is present and it\u2019s being sold in used, rough-condition form, but it offers good value for a buyer who wants something affordable with practical potential.",
